notes.p: "Kinetic Analysis Shows that Vitamin A Disposal Rate in Humans is Positively Correlated with Vitamin A Stores" by Chris Cifelli and friends (2008)
The original model was coded in WinSAAM. There the delay compartments were modelled as a series of connected pseudo-compartments. We use the same approach here.
The model includes a helper parameter EXPERIMENT. Setting EXPERIMENT=1 simulates China, EXPERIMENT=2 simulates USA.
Note that this model reimplementation does NOT predict the steady states presented in Table 3.
